  Death glided across the hall. He had been trained by the best assains back 
on cybertron. He was almost impossible to hear. He also had the ability to 
tap into a bot data tracks. He waled past the bridge and noticed Phobia. He 
scanned his tracks and found horrible things. He decided to kill the bug. He 
glided across the bridge floor. He stood behind Phobia..(remember he is very 
very diff to hear.) He pulled his reaper and proceeded to cut off the bots 
head......
